*hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.3 (04 Apr 2015)

  04 Apr 2015; Mark Wright <gienah@gentoo.org> +hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.3.ebuild,
  -hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r1.ebuild, hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Bump hdbc-postgresql to 2.3.2.3. Drop hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r1 as it was
  replaced by hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r2. Add :* to the hdbc-
  postgresql-2.3.2.2-r2 dependency dev-db/postgresql-7:*

  28 Dec 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org>
  hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.1.ebuild, hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r1.ebuild,
  hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Rename virtual/postgresql to dev-db/postgresql

  04 Nov 2014; Aaron W. Swenson <titanofold@gentoo.org>
  hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.1.ebuild, hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r1.ebuild,
  hdbc-postgresql-2.3.2.2-r2.ebuild:
  Update PostgreSQL dependencies and/or checks to virtual/postgresql.

